## Context
This is a Spring Boot 3.4.5 + Java 21 project adding document tagging. Tasks 1-4 are already done (DB migration, entities, mappers, services, ROs, VOs). Now you need to create the Manager layer and Controller.

Key patterns from the existing Star feature:
- Controller: @ApiResource(path="/node/xxx") + @PostResource(path="/method", requiredPermission=false, externalOnly=true)
- Manager split into query/update with interface + impl
- SessionContext.getUserId() for current user
- ExceptionUtil.isNotNull/isNull/isTrue for assertions
- SpaceNodeException enum for error codes
- ResponseData.success(result) for responses
- @Transactional on methods that do multiple writes
- SpaceNodeTransfer.toSpaceNodeVoWithRole() for enriching VOs

Already created (you can use these directly, they exist):
- SpaceNodeTagEntity, SpaceNodeTagRelEntity, SpaceNodeEntity (with visibilityTag field)
- SpaceNodeTagMapper, SpaceNodeTagRelMapper
- ISpaceNodeTagService: listBySpaceIdAndUserId(spaceId, userId), getBySpaceIdAndUserIdAndName(spaceId, userId, name)
- ISpaceNodeTagRelService: listBySpaceNodeIdAndUserId, listBySpaceNodeIdsAndUserId, listByTagId, getBySpaceNodeIdAndTagId, listSpaceNodeIdsByTagIdAndUserId
- ISpaceNodeService: getById, updateById, listByIds (existing)
- CreateTagRo, UpdateTagRo, BindTagRo, UnbindTagRo, SetVisibilityTagRo, TagNodeQueryRo (extends BasePageRo with pageNum/pageSize)
- SpaceNodeTagVo (id, name, color, sortOrder)
- SpaceNodeVo (has visibilityTag and tags fields)
- SpaceNodeException: TAG_NOT_EXIST(620), TAG_NAME_DUPLICATE(621), TAG_NOT_OWNER(622), TAG_ALREADY_BINDNODE(623), TAG_NOT_BINDNODE(624), NOT_EXIST(601)
- SpaceNodeTransfer has toSpaceNodeVoWithRole(List) method

